ZH: 他出生在一个赤贫的家庭。
EN: He was born into a very poor family.

ZH: 她从小就过着赤贫的生活。
EN: She has been living a life of extreme poverty since childhood.

ZH: 那个地区的人们大部分都是赤贫的。
EN: Most of the people in that region are extremely poor.

ZH: 这个村子里的人们生活在赤贫中。
EN: The people in this village live in dire poverty.

ZH: 这个孩子出身赤贫，但他努力向上。
EN: This child came from poverty, but he works hard to get ahead.

ZH: 赤贫并没有阻挡他追求成功。
EN: Extreme poverty did not stop him from pursuing success.

ZH: 这个国家有人生活在赤贫线以下。
EN: There are people living below the poverty line in this country.

ZH: 孩子们每天都为了不再赤贫而努力学习。
EN: The children study hard every day to escape from extreme poverty.

ZH: 赤贫的条件下，健康问题变得更加严重。
EN: Health issues become even more severe under conditions of extreme poverty.

ZH: 这个社区缺乏基本的设施，赤贫现象十分普遍。
EN: The community lacks basic amenities, and extreme poverty is widespread.

ZH: 尽管赤贫，他仍然保持乐观的态度。
EN: Despite extreme poverty, he maintains an optimistic attitude.

ZH: 这个地区的赤贫状况引起了国际社会的关注。
EN: The extreme poverty situation in this region has attracted international attention.

ZH: 我们应该努力帮助那些赤贫的人们脱离困境。
EN: We should make efforts to help those who are in extreme poverty to escape their predicament.

ZH: 这个城市的赤贫问题亟待解决。
EN: The issue of extreme poverty in this city needs to be urgently addressed.

ZH: 他们被赤贫所逼，只能靠乞讨来生存。
EN: They are forced into begging for survival due to extreme poverty.

ZH: 他们的日常生活里没有赤贫的痕迹。
EN: There is no trace of extreme poverty in their daily lives.

ZH: 赤贫给他们带来了无尽的痛苦和困扰。
EN: Extreme poverty has brought them endless pain and suffering.

ZH: 他们正努力摆脱赤贫的命运。
EN: They are working hard to escape the fate of extreme poverty.

ZH: 社会应该共同努力，减少赤贫人口的数量。
EN: Society should make joint efforts to reduce the number of people living in extreme poverty.

ZH: 这个国家通过多项政策成功减少了赤贫人口。
EN: This country has successfully reduced the number of people living in extreme poverty through various policies.
